        <span class="numeracion">1</span>
        <div class="how-step2 clearfix">
          <h2>Identify your skills, talents and passions to define your philanthropic project</h2>
          <p>Think about a change you would really like to see in your community. Think about a cause to which you would like to contribute. Think about your skills, your educational goals, your talents, and how you can or are using these characteristics to make the world around you a better place. Choose a way that you can add up.
          </p>
          <div class="diagram">
            <%= image_tag "how/student1.png" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div  id="row5" class="row clearfix">
