        <div class="how-step2 clearfix">
          <h2>Make a profile that tells the world about you and your educational and philanthropic goals</h2>
          <p>Go to (link for application) to create your profile and share a little bit about who you are, your educational goals, why you care about adding up, and why you believe you have the capacity to do so. Make a short video about your social project. Choose 3-5 pictures that show potential sponsors the real you. Sign the Honor Code (link to Honor Code). Pay $25 and go live!
          </p>
          <div class="diagram">
            <%= image_tag "how/student2.png" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
